Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:32.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:37.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to do it for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun are the chariots of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:47.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,They won't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's—!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald... Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:05.93,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The Ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, come and take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:48.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you adjust the communicator valve pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, can someone help me pull this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's great working here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, people. First of all, we have to go over every inch of every Simoun to check for damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Yes, sir!\N— Already on it, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:05.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,So, how's the old nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:15.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You look like you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,We only just got back, but you already look as busy as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:26.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. We were told to get the Simoun repaired as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,'Scuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:37.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could you come look over the elevators?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.14,0:03:41.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla, I hope I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:55.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Plumbum and Argentum are allies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:59.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before they launch an offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:06.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks like we'll have to make another difficult request of the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, not a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:10.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,An order, Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything we've gone through has been my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything has happened because of my selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:27.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Trying to forget Amuria and the Emerald Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,What foolishness is this, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:55.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are so many things you mustn't forget, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura and Limone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're gone, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:29.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon failed, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seriously, don't you think that those two just ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thinking that might make it easier to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:47.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,However, the important thing is not the reason, but the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:51.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've lost more of our precious friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,So, we're finally back on the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't see how you can be so happy about it, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Are you saying you're not, Alti?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:12.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're roomies now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need to get along with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:54.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,As for the many things that have happened to you, I deeply—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:07:00.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Twelve Simoun from Chor Rubor and Chor Caput were destroyed in the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:03.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Central Command hasn't been able to find replacements for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:10.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now, the only choir aboard the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} is yours, Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:14.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your Eminence, what about the members of Chor Caput and Chor Rubor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Most of their sibyllae have gone to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Relieved of their posts, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep your mouth shut, Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the truth, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,They don't need us if we're not flying a Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:37.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, these is someone here who would like to speak to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:08.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae of Chor Tempest, allow me to welcome you back once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:12.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:18.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Limone and Sibylla Dominura are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:20.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're on a course for the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:28.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are we heading to the Ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not a place you can just—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is true, Sibylla Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:39.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins are the holiest site in the entire Holy Land of Simulacrum. They are a forbidden place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}must{\i0} reach the Ruins before the forces of the Alliance, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:56.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it, Sibylla Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this mission mandatory?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:13.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are the only ones in the entire Theocracy who can accomplish—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is not a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:20.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, your participation in this mission is mandatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Does this mean that we can't even go to the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:33.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think there is anywhere left for us to run any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:34.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that I would have the opportunity to speak to you like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:40.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril is no longer a child to whom I can give orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:45.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is nothing more that I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please don't speak that way, Mr. Vice-Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:50.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am grateful for how much you've looked after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:57.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking that you've changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Boy, you really saved our necks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:30.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} hadn't arrived,\Nthe {\i1}Messis{\i0} would have been done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you for all your hard work. I am glad that we made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:42.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was unable to safely return all the priestesses you entrusted to my care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please accept my deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain Wauf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:54.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll get your full report later, but Sibylla Dominura and Sibylla Limone—?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:57.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe that they are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then, what happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:09.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,But perhaps we'll find the answer at the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:43.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Neviril?\N— What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um... nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,This must be hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:22.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are others for whom this is harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:02.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,We will proceed as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:16.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest will enter at low altitude, with our speaker cables attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:21.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our mission objective is to protect the Ruins from the alliance between Plumbum and Argentum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,So these are the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:58.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is my first time here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Tempus Spatium's holy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, it doesn't look like the enemy's here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't lower your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, where does she get off talking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Two o'clock low!
Comment: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:12.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:23.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, are those—?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:30.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:31.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neither have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:34.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll take the one on the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do they intend to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Shark Ri Maajon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have to chase them, Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't let those things get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:18.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who is operating those Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who is {\i1}praying to the skies{\i0} with those Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how are they able to fly like {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are they the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're shooting at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:47.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Why are we fighting other Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Worry about that later, Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:55.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's leave the pursuit to the others, and investigate the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:07.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,My music box—it's playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's closed, but it's playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:47.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,They got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Return to the Ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:02.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:08.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's up? A minute ago, you said you didn't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look, they're trying to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:36.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:01.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,We hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:06.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,We finally got one, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:17.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Sibylla Neviril and Sibylla Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:29.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:32.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is Onashia here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,And at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's flying that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:52.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's something very strange about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Onashia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why is this place the same as the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:19.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus watched over the flow of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:23.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,and Spatium placed people where they belonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:24.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,The two became a pair,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:29.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,and gave the people unending blessings... and terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:44.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:58.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:01.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is going on in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:13.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:18.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here in this place, all of time and space...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:24.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...all of it is released from the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Yun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:41.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:45.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:52.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I don't think this place just {\i1}looks like{\i0} the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? What do you mean,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:22:00.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,This place... this place {\i1}is{\i0} the Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just like Grandpa said!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:19.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Angulas?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,AA - E - RU !!!
